&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Sphere Entertainment Co. is a leader in immersive experiences, technology and media. The Company includes Sphere, an experiential medium powered by advanced technologies. The first Sphere opened in Las Vegas, with a second venue planned for Abu Dhabi. In addition, the Company includes MSG Networks, which operates two regional sports and entertainment networks, MSG Network and MSG Sportsnet, as well as a direct-to-consumer and authenticated streaming product, MSG+, delivering a wide range of live sports content and other programming. More information is available at&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nam12.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sphereentertainmentco.com%2F&amp;amp;data=05%7C02%7CMaddie.Rizzo%40msg.com%7Cf345c42af5d7463ff83408de643f07ae%7Cf2c1e8475bd24ba2b5e4b529a645f31a%7C1%7C0%7C639058419051444527%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;amp;sdata=cMiSC0m9pVYooMKOmqGRKLvrWz4pyLwUcbtd%2BD8jl0E%3D&amp;amp;reserved=0&quot; data-auth=&quot;NotApplicable&quot; data-linkindex=&quot;3&quot;&gt;www.sphereentertainmentco.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we hiring? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;The Account Executive will support the Director and Group Sales Manager(s) on the Group Sales team with a primary focus on prospecting group sales leads and managing inbound group sales inquiries for Sphere. The Account Executive will also perform administrative responsibilities relating to group sales at Sphere.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you do? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Meet or exceed all revenue and ticket sales goals assigned.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Consistently exceed daily and weekly touchpoint goals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Manage inbound lead queue and phone line and respond to all inquiries in a timely manner.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Proactively source new leads via outbound sales activities including cold calling to create sales opportunities for the group sales team with a focus on B2B sales&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Effectively manage and track all sales, inventory adjustments, activity and client and prospect interaction through proper databases and administrative systems in a timely manner.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Leverage sales accelerating technology and tools provided to increase overall efficiency and production.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Participate in sales meetings, training sessions, and other professional development opportunities to enhance sales skills and product knowledge.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Provide excellent customer service to all guests&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;

