&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;The Building Engineer supports MSG Sphere with the daily operation of all building systems and will be engaged in operating, maintaining, and repairing all facility system equipment and machinery associated with HVAC, mechanical, electrical systems and will ensure to identify best practices for a safe and efficient environment for guests and employees.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;The Building Engineer will be qualified to perform service and repair of HVAC equipment, motors, pumps, air compressors, ice and refrigerating machines, boilers, exhaust fans, cooling towers and plumbing systems. Additionally, the building engineer will operate and monitor BMS, fire alarm, power monitoring, and lighting control systems and provide continuous documentation of alterations, maintenance, and repair.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you do? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Service&lt;em&gt;, &lt;/em&gt;maintain&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;and&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;repair&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;HVAC&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;and refrigeration equipment, pumps, exhaust fans, air handlers, mini split AC units, boilers and all associated valves and controllers. Inspect and replace air filters&lt;em&gt;, &lt;/em&gt;belts, bearings, and water filtration equipment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Perform plumbing repairs on all bathroom fixtures and valves both manual and automatic including toilets lavatories and urinals. Service all drain lines and operate drain cleaning machines, augers and water jet drain cleaning equipment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Perform lighting repairs and troubleshoot lighting control circuits including drivers, dimmers, relays and wall stations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Service, maintain and repair kitchen and food service equipment, beverage dispensing systems, walk in coolers, and ice machines.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
