&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Prepare display sell products to patrons in a friendly and courteous manner.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Assist patrons in their selection of merchandise by answering any questions they may have.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Assist concession, and bar supervisors in the set-up of the assigned selling area.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Process credit card charge transactions for food/beverage selling areas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Walking and selling various food &amp;amp; beverage items throughout the Sphere front-of-house.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Verify point of sale terminal financials and reconcile with stand lead and/or supervisor by location.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Completes daily and nightly inventory.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Notify the stand lead and/or supervisors of product that requires replenishment during the course of an event.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
