&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Sphere Entertainment Co. is a leader in immersive experiences, technology and media. The Company includes Sphere, an experiential medium powered by advanced technologies. The first Sphere opened in Las Vegas, with a second venue planned for Abu Dhabi. In addition, the Company includes MSG Networks, which operates two regional sports and entertainment networks, MSG Network and MSG Sportsnet, as well as a direct-to-consumer and authenticated streaming product, MSG+, delivering a wide range of live sports content and other programming. More information is available at&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nam12.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sphereentertainmentco.com%2F&amp;amp;data=05%7C02%7CMaddie.Rizzo%40msg.com%7Cf345c42af5d7463ff83408de643f07ae%7Cf2c1e8475bd24ba2b5e4b529a645f31a%7C1%7C0%7C639058419051444527%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;amp;sdata=cMiSC0m9pVYooMKOmqGRKLvrWz4pyLwUcbtd%2BD8jl0E%3D&amp;amp;reserved=0&quot; data-auth=&quot;NotApplicable&quot; data-linkindex=&quot;3&quot;&gt;www.sphereentertainmentco.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we hiring? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enthusiastic, skilled and reliable Generative Artist with passion for creating using AI to enable content creation for the largest screens in the world!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This Generative Artist reports to the Generative Effects Supervisor and works across every aspect of AI-driven production: prompt engineering, asset preparation, nodegraph based creation tools, post processing of Gen AI outputs, compositing workflows, etc. with expert level skills in one or more of those areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working closely with leadership in Creative, Design, Production, Post Production, Visual Effects, Playback and Experiential Production, this position is ideal for innovative artists who are good communicators with a positive attitude and great creative problem solving skills.&amp;nbsp; This role is part of a Generative Effects team exploring and developing a new and unique language for Sphere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What will you do? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute creative briefs by generating, iterating, and refining AI outputs to meet directorial needs and creative vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write and refine prompts to feed into Gen AI models, running tools like or similar to ComfyUI and iterating on outputs to match directorial notes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create start and end frames in Photoshop and other Gen AI tools to establish creative direction for sequences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform post-processing and compositing of AI-generated imagery in Nuke, combining generative outputs with traditional production techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Publish versioned assets to ShotGrid for supervisor review and approval.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain organized asset libraries, file naming conventions, and version control within the team&#39;s production environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively run Gen AI tests in collaboration with the Sr. Director of Production &amp;amp; AI Innovation and the GenFX Supervisor.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver final output at scale, working within production cadence and meeting deadlines across multiple sequences or projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current with emerging Gen AI models, techniques, and tools, incorporating advancements into daily workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the GenFX Supervisor to refine workflows, troubleshoot outputs, and maintain quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
